node.text:
This image was licensed by a puzzle company to make a jigsaw 🧩 out of. When they asked I was like that’s honestly so cool and of course I would love to do that . Found out today the samples are on their way. The puzzle will be stocked at select target stores (i believe in the US) as well as Amazon . Will formally update you and post about it once I receive the puzzle !
-
I learnt so many random things about what makes a good puzzle eg. Did you know blank spaces =not good 😌 (unless you are going for like one of those all same colour ones)….because a puzzler needs to be challenged by having each piece as unique . 
-
